The Cutedoll     Home Page(首页)     Doll Series(系列玩偶)    

The Cutedoll company has a wide range of dolls, such as:
(The Cutedoll公司旗下有众多系列玩偶，例如)

  • Struggle Rabbit(奋斗兔)

    •         With the resolute expression and the attitude of rolling up the sleeves to show the spirit of struggle, it has become a photo tool for
    many star talents.

            以坚毅的表情和撸起袖子的姿态展现奋斗精神，成为众多明星达人的拍照出街神器。

  • Goblin(小妖怪)

    •         From "Journey to the West", debut is out of the circle, contrast ugly and cute "rushing son" incarnation of workers for mouth, let
    countless workers harvest spiritual comfort.

            源自《西游记》，出道即出圈，反差丑萌的“奔波儿灞”化身打工人嘴替，让无数打工人收
    获精神慰藉。

  • The leader(龙头老大)

    •         Launched at the beginning of the year, the "Leading Boss" series of dolls has become one of the most popular zodiac dolls in 2024
    with the extremely Oriental bearing of Jia Chen Green Dragon and innovative expression and shape design.

            年初推出的“龙头老大”系列玩偶，以极具东方气度的甲辰青龙与创新的表情、造型设计，成为2024年极火爆的生肖玩偶之一。
